Description:
    Generates a new Me Salva! customized controller at app/controllers.
    Pass the controller name as an argument, either CamelCased or snake_cased.
    It is possible to pass the attributes arguments as well.

Examples:
    `bin/rails generate ms_controller Awesome`
    `bin/rails generate ms_controller Awesome attribute1:string attribute2:integer attribute3:references`

    creates a Me Salva! customized awesome controller:
        app/controllers/awesome_controller.rb
